Interface WriteableComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Component, ReadableComponent
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    TextInputComponent, TextInputMultiComponent, ValueSetComponent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TextInputComponentImpl, TextInputMultiComponentImpl, ValueSetComponentImpl, WriteableComponentImpl

    public interface WriteableComponent
extends ReadableComponent
    A representation of the model object 'Writeable Component'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Ceil
    • Floor
